cowboy
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a young worker employed to milk house cows and assist in maintaining the homestead supplies of wood, fruit, vegetables etc.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
